			<CASNumber>7681-57-4</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Sodium metabisulfite is a type of sulfite additive used as a preservative and antioxidant to prevent browning and discoloration during food preparation and distribution. It is often found in wine and dried fruits and used as a biscuit/pastry dough softening agent. It is also used in the commercial wine making, paper and textile industry as a bleaching agent. However, it can be associated with serious allergic reactions.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">焦亚硫酸钠是一种亚硫酸盐添加剂，用作防腐剂和抗氧化剂，以防止食品在制备和销售过程中变色。它常出现在葡萄酒和干果中，还可用作饼干/糕点面团软化剂。它还被用作商业酿酒、造纸和纺织业的漂白剂。不过，它可能会引起严重的过敏反应。</common:generalComment>
